@DATABASE "Sai Combat"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - S - Sai Combat"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - S
                   ====================================

                                Sai Combat
                                ==========



DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Lives = x" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(32421,255)"}               32421,x (x= 1-255)


                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).

                         This POKE corrupts the bottom of the screen,
                         but there's not a lot can be done about it.

                         Rastan.
@endnode
